      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MOSCOW CHICK (1) was a last-start winner from the rails at Broken Hill over 525m (30.30), scoring by 4 lengths. Drawn the rails again and rates the measuring stick. LEGS ELEVEN (2) broke a string of placings finishing in the money four on end before a last start fourth (30.92) at Angle Park. The form from her last run stacks up well. Should be about the money. PAW LOUIS (4) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at Angle Park behind Apilla (43.07) in a OPEN. Stalked the pace but found the line strongly. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Expected to feature. NITRO NEO (8) is a last-start placegetter when at the top of betting - in the mix again.",
